text: Gada or Gadha may refer to: *Gada (mace), an ancient Indian club *Gada, Nigeria, a Local Government Area in Sokoto State *Gadha, Nepal, a village development committee in Siraha District, Nepal *Gadha (album), a 1998 album by Chandrabindoo *Gadaa, an Oromo self-governance system *Garha/GADA, a Muslim caste of India *Gadā, the pen name of a Chaghatay poet == See also == * Gada River (disambiguation)
title: Gada
